OL,3,CFamily of man murdered alongside wife
OL,4,Cin Sussex vow to honour couple's legacy
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's James Dunham
OL,7,Fcaught up with the family at the start
OL,8,Fof their fundraising challenge to
OL,9,Fhonour their loved ones
OL,11,FThe family of a man who was murdered
OL,12,Falongside his wife have vowed to
OL,13,Fcreate a legacy for them.
OL,15,FIn June 2023, parents-of-four Josh
OL,16,FBashford, 33, and Chloe Bashford, 30,
OL,17,Fwere found dead at their home in
OL,18,FNewhaven, East Sussex.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
