PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781021473
OL,3,CFamily of man murdered alongside wife
OL,4,Cin Sussex vow to honour couple's legacy
OL,6,FChloe's stepfather, 67-year-old Derek
OL,7,FMartin, was sentenced to at least 29
OL,8,Fyears in jail for their murder.
OL,10,FThree years on since Josh and Chloe
OL,11,Fwere killed, Josh's siblings and his
OL,12,Ffather have completed a gruelling non-
OL,13,Fstop 66 mile walk that began in
OL,14,FCroydon and ended on the south coast.
OL,16,FJosh's sister Tasha said: "It doesn't
OL,17,Ffeel real that it's three years now.
OL,18,FIt still feels like we're stuck in
OL,19,Fthat day but the world is still
OL,20,Fcontinuing to go on so we have no
OL,21,Fchoice."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781021473
OL,3,CFamily of man murdered alongside wife
OL,4,Cin Sussex vow to honour couple's legacy
OL,6,FBilly Bashford, Josh's brother, said:
OL,7,F"I think a lot of us are still
OL,8,Fgrieving, I know I am especially.
OL,10,F"I think Josh and Chloe would be proud
OL,11,Fthat they're seeing us do something
OL,12,Ffor them."
OL,14,FTheir challenge aimed to raise funds
OL,15,Ffor Victim Support, a charity
OL,16,Fproviding life-long help to people
OL,17,Fwhose loved ones have been killed.
OL,19,FThe family say the charity has helped
OL,20,Fnavigate them on their painful journey
OL,21,Finto a new normal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781021473
OL,3,CFamily of man murdered alongside wife
OL,4,Cin Sussex vow to honour couple's legacy
OL,6,FTasha said: "For how vital that
OL,7,Fservice has been to me, to us, to my
OL,8,Ffamily - to know it's going to happen
OL,9,Fto other people sadly - it's going to
OL,10,Fhelp those people."
OL,12,FBilly said: "They've been there
OL,13,Fthrough the darkest of times for us as
OL,14,Fa family, I think to give something
OL,15,Fback to Victim Support, it feels like
OL,16,Fwe've done something."
OL,18,FHaving sat through a heavy and
OL,19,Femotional court trial, the family are
OL,20,Fnow focused on the future and
OL,21,Fhonouring Josh and Chloe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
